<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UPay | Link Expired</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @theme {
            --color-upay-blue: #2563eb;
            --color-upay-error: #ef4444;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 100% 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.03) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 0% 100%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.03) 0px, transparent 50%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4 font-sans text-slate-900">

    <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden text-center">
        
        <div class="h-2 bg-red-500"></div>

        <div class="p-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-6">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-red-100">
                    <i data-lucide="link-2-off" class="text-red-500 w-10 h-10"></i>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Link Unavailable</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">
                    The password reset link you clicked is either **expired**, **already used**, or has been **modified**.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-5 mb-8 border border-slate-100">
                <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">What happened?</h3>
                <ul class="text-left text-xs text-slate-600 space-y-3">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Security links for UPay expire after 60 minutes.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="shield-alert" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>The link can only be used once to prevent unauthorized access.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
                <a href="/user/forgot-password" class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20">
                    Request New Link
                </a>
                
                <a href="/user/login" class="block w-full bg-transparent hover:bg-slate-50 text-slate-500 font-medium py-3 rounded-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200">
                    Back to Sign In
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 py-4 border-t border-slate-100">
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400">
                Need help? <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Contact UPay Support</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
